class Route {
    constructor(
        id, 
        name,
        mountainId, 
        gain,
        distance,
        difficulty,
        risk,
        ){
            this.id = id,
            this.name = name,
            this.mountainId= mountainId,
            this.gain = gain,
            this.distance = distance,
            this.difficulty = difficulty,
            this.risk = risk
    }
}

export default Route
